---
import Base from '../../layouts/Base.astro';
---
<Base title="Beautiful Losers — Michalina Sablik">
  <div class="container page-content">
    <h1>Beautiful Losers</h1>
    <p class="exhibition-detail-venue">Jak Zapomnieć Gallery, Kraków | 2020</p>
    <div class="exhibition-detail-body">
      <p>Inspired by Leonard Cohen's 1966 novel, widely regarded as pioneering Canadian surrealist literature. Explored themes of spiritual seeking, escapism, and contemporary expressions of idealism through works combining intellectual and visual collage elements.</p>
      <p>Presented diverse contemporary mediums: VR-generated spiritual worlds, color crayon post-humanist imagery, soft-sculpted crocheted installations referencing indigenous totems, abstract compositions, and vaporwave video.</p>
    </div>
    <div class="exhibition-detail-credits">
      <p><strong>Artists:</strong> Sam Balfus, Marcin Janusz, Aleksandra Liput, Zofia Pałucha, Schwestern Sisters (Tea Stražičić, Marta Stražičić), Strahinja Arbutina</p>
      <p><strong>Curators:</strong> DZIDY (Michalina Sablik, Aleksandra Liput)</p>
    </div>
    <div class="exhibition-gallery" style="margin-top: 2.5rem; display: grid; gap: 1rem;">
      <img src="/images/exhibitions/beautiful-loosers/1.jpg" alt="Exhibition view" loading="lazy" style="width:100%; border-radius: 4px;" />
